name: Global X Equal Weight Canadian Groceries & Staples Index ETF
longDescription: MART uses the Mirae Asset Equal Weight Canadian Groceries & Staples Index as its Underlying Index. The Mirae Asset Equal Weight Canadian Groceries & Staples Index includes the largest TSX-listed securities of Canadian food and staples retail companies. Holding companies are ineligible for inclusion.
fulldescription: MART uses the Mirae Asset Equal Weight Canadian Groceries & Staples Index as its Underlying Index. The Mirae Asset Equal Weight Canadian Groceries & Staples Index includes the largest TSX-listed securities of Canadian food and staples retail companies. Holding companies are ineligible for inclusion. Constituents are subject to minimum market capitalization and liquidity screens MART seeks to replicate, to the extent possible and net of expenses, the performance of an equalweighted index designed to provide exposure to the largest Canadian food and staples retail companies (currently, the Mirae Asset Equal Weight Canadian Groceries  Staples Index)
